'''賓布菈赤翅蟲'''（''Binburrum''）是[[鞘翅目|鞘翅目]][[赤翅蟲科|赤翅蟲科]]下的一屬，該屬成員僅見於[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Hsiao|first=Yun|last2=Pollock|first2=Darren A.|date=December 2020|title=Contribution to the knowledge of the endemic Australian genus Binburrum Pollock, 1995 (Coleoptera: Pyrochroidae: Pilipalpinae), with description of three new species|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/canadian-entomologist/article/abs/contribution-to-the-knowledge-of-the-endemic-australian-genus-binburrum-pollock-1995-coleoptera-pyrochroidae-pilipalpinae-with-description-of-three-new-species/D9782DFAEEF63A38915484E7CD532F46|journal=The Canadian Entomologist|language=en|volume=153|issue=2|pages=244–256|doi=10.4039/tce.2020.74|issn=0008-347X|access-date=2021-04-12|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412064602/https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/canadian-entomologist/article/abs/contribution-to-the-knowledge-of-the-endemic-australian-genus-binburrum-pollock-1995-coleoptera-pyrochroidae-pilipalpinae-with-description-of-three-new-species/D9782DFAEEF63A38915484E7CD532F46|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 特徵 ==
中小型甲蟲（體長通常小於9毫米），翅鞘兩側外緣平行。頭部及前胸背板上佈有粗凹點刻。觸角絲狀，第四小節較二、三小節加起來的長度為短。緣摺（elytral epipleuron）從吻端延伸至翅鞘前3/4<ref name=":0" />。

== 棲息地 ==
幼蟲主要棲息於枯木的潮濕樹皮下，已記錄的植物物種包含{{tsl|en|Phyllocladus aspleniifolius|芹葉松}}等<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Family Pyrochroidae - Fire-Colored Beetles|url=https://bugguide.net/node/view/9123|access-date=2021-03-24|website=bugguide.net|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505050641/https://bugguide.net/node/view/9123|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=M|first=Yee|date=2018|title=Not all dead wood is the same - a selection error reveals an unusual emergence of beetles from decaying celerytop pine logs|url=https://eprints.utas.edu.au/32143/|journal=Tasmanian Naturalist|volume=141|pages=83–91|access-date=2021-04-12|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412064543/https://eprints.utas.edu.au/32143/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。成蟲則主要分布於葉片或光源附近<ref name=":2" />。

